<item>
            <title>[SPARK-38488] Spark doc build not work on Mac OS M1</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-38488</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
diff --git a/docs/.bundle/config b/docs/.bundle/config
index b13821f801..68c1ee493a 100644
--- a/docs/.bundle/config
+++ b/docs/.bundle/config
@@ -1,2 +1,3 @@
&#160;---
&#160;BUNDLE_PATH: &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;.local_ruby_bundle&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
+BUNDLE_BUILD__FFI: &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;--enable-libffi-alloc&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
diff --git a/docs/Gemfile b/docs/Gemfile
index f991622708..6c35201296 100644
--- a/docs/Gemfile
+++ b/docs/Gemfile
@@ -17,6 +17,7 @@
&#160;source &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;https:&lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;//rubygems.org&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;+gem &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;ffi&quot;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;1.15.5&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
&#160;gem &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;jekyll&quot;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;4.2.1&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
&#160;gem &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;rouge&quot;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;3.26.0&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
 gem &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;jekyll-redirect-from&quot;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;0.16.0&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;After above patch redo `bundle install`, then it works, you could see this as ref if you meet the same issue.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;will take a deep look to solve this.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

